snippet.title: ANIMAL WELL Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam and PlayStation Store!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/813230/ANIMAL_WELL/
https://playstation.com/en-us/games/animal-well/

Explore a dense interconnected labyrinth, and unravel its many secrets. Collect items to manipulate your environment in surprising and meaningful ways. Encounter creatures both beautiful and unsettling, and try to survive what lurks in the dark. In Animal Well there is more than what you see.

Learn more at: www.animalwell.net/

Follow along on:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/animal_well
Discord: https://discord.gg/PYNDg2xe3J
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/animalwellgame/
